A video of a hippo attacking a vehicle has gone viral on social media, reports the Pretoria East Rekord. The video shows a man slowing down when he spots a baby hippo on the side of the road. When the hippo spots the man, he charges at the Ford Ranger bakkie, damaging the front of it. According to some comments, the incident took place on the bridge of the Jozini Dam/Pongolapoort Dam in northern KwaZulu-Natal. Caxton News Service